text: Altmärkische Höhe is a municipality of the district of Stendal, in Saxony- Anhalt, Germany. It was created on 1 January 2010 and consists of the former municipalities of Boock, Bretsch, Gagel, Heiligenfelde, Kossebau, Losse and Lückstedt.
